msgid "Using RigidBody"
msgstr "Ag baint úsáide as RigidBody"

msgid "What is a rigid body?"
msgstr "Cad is comhlacht docht ann?"

msgid ""
"A rigid body is one that is directly controlled by the physics engine in "
"order to simulate the behavior of physical objects. In order to define the "
"shape of the body, it must have one or more :ref:`Shape3D <class_Shape3D>` "
"objects assigned. Note that setting the position of these shapes will affect "
"the body's center of mass."
msgstr ""
"Is éard is comhlacht docht ann ná ceann atá á rialú go díreach ag inneall na "
"fisice chun iompar rudaí fisiceacha a insamhail. Chun cruth an choirp a "
"shainiú, caithfidh sé ceann amháin nó níos mó :ref:`Shape3D <class_Shape3D>` "
"réada sannta. Tabhair faoi deara go gcuirfidh suíomh na gcruthanna seo "
"isteach ar lárionad maise an choirp."

msgid "How to control a rigid body"
msgstr "Conas comhlacht docht a rialú"

msgid ""
"A rigid body's behavior can be altered by setting its properties, such as "
"mass and weight. A physics material needs to be added to the rigid body to "
"adjust its friction and bounce, and set if it's absorbent and/or rough. "
"These properties can be set in the Inspector or via code. See :ref:"
"`RigidBody3D <class_RigidBody3D>` and :ref:`PhysicsMaterial "
"<class_PhysicsMaterial>` for the full list of properties and their effects."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir iompar comhlacht docht a athrú trína chuid airíonna a shocrú, "
"amhail mais agus meáchan. Ní mór ábhar fisice a chur leis an gcorp docht "
"chun a fhrithchuimilte agus a phreab a choigeartú, agus a shocrú an bhfuil "
"sé súiteach agus/nó garbh. Is féidir na maoine seo a shocrú sa Chigire nó "
"trí chód. Féach :ref:`RigidBody3D <class_RigidBody3D>` agus :tag:"
"`PhysicsMaterial <class_PhysicsMaterial>` le haghaidh liosta iomlán na n-"
"airíonna agus a n-éifeachtaí."

msgid ""
"There are several ways to control a rigid body's movement, depending on your "
"desired application."
msgstr ""
"Tá roinnt bealaí ann chun gluaiseacht comhlacht docht a rialú, ag brath ar "
"d'iarratas atá ag teastáil."

msgid ""
"If you only need to place a rigid body once, for example to set its initial "
"location, you can use the methods provided by the :ref:`Node3D "
"<class_Node3D>` node, such as ``set_global_transform()`` or ``look_at()``. "
"However, these methods cannot be called every frame or the physics engine "
"will not be able to correctly simulate the body's state. As an example, "
"consider a rigid body that you want to rotate so that it points towards "
"another object. A common mistake when implementing this kind of behavior is "
"to use ``look_at()`` every frame, which breaks the physics simulation. "
"Below, we'll demonstrate how to implement this correctly."
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil uait ach corp docht a chur uair amháin, mar shampla chun a "
"shuíomh tosaigh a shocrú, is féidir leat úsáid a bhaint as na modhanna a "
"sholáthraíonn an nód :ref:`Node3D <class_Node3D>`, mar `` "
"set_global_transform()`` nó `` breathnú_ar()``. Mar sin féin, ní féidir gach "
"fráma a thabhairt ar na modhanna seo nó ní bheidh inneall na fisice in ann "
"staid an choirp a insamhladh i gceart. Mar shampla, smaoinigh ar chorp docht "
"ar mhaith leat a rothlú ionas go díríonn sé ar rud eile. Botún coitianta "
"agus an cineál seo iompair á chur i bhfeidhm is ea ``look_at()`` a úsáid i "
"ngach fráma, a bhriseann an insamhalta fisice. Anseo thíos, taispeánfaimid "
"conas é seo a chur i bhfeidhm i gceart."

msgid ""
"The fact that you can't use ``set_global_transform()`` or ``look_at()`` "
"methods doesn't mean that you can't have full control of a rigid body. "
"Instead, you can control it by using the ``_integrate_forces()`` callback. "
"In this method, you can add *forces*, apply *impulses*, or set the "
"*velocity* in order to achieve any movement you desire."
msgstr ""
"Ós rud é nach féidir leat modhanna ''set_global_transform()'' nó "
"''look_at()'' a úsáid, ní chiallaíonn sé sin nach féidir leat smacht iomlán "
"a bheith agat ar chorp docht. Ina áit sin, is féidir leat é a rialú tríd an "
"aisghlaoch ''_integrate_forces()'' a úsáid. Sa mhodh seo, is féidir leat "
"*forces *a chur leis, *impulses *a chur i bhfeidhm, nó an *velocity *a "
"shocrú chun aon ghluaiseacht is mian leat a bhaint amach."

msgid "The \"look at\" method"
msgstr "An modh \"féach ar\""

msgid ""
"As described above, using the Node3D's ``look_at()`` method can't be used "
"each frame to follow a target. Here is a custom ``look_at()`` method called "
"``look_follow()`` that will work with rigid bodies:"
msgstr ""
"Mar a thuairiscítear thuas, ní féidir úsáid a bhaint as modh ''look_at()'' "
"Node3D chun sprioc a leanúint. Seo modh saincheaptha ''look_at()'' ar a "
"dtugtar ''look_follow()'' a oibreoidh le comhlachtaí dochta:"

msgid ""
"This method uses the rigid body's ``angular_velocity`` property to rotate "
"the body. The axis to rotate around is given by the cross product between "
"the current forward direction and the direction one wants to look in. The "
"``clamp`` is a simple method used to prevent the amount of rotation from "
"going past the direction which is wanted to be looked in, as the total "
"amount of rotation needed is given by the arccosine of the dot product. This "
"method can be used with ``axis_lock_angular_*`` as well. If more precise "
"control is needed, solutions such as ones relying on :ref:`class_Quaternion` "
"may be required, as discussed in :ref:`doc_using_transforms`."
msgstr ""
"Úsáideann an modh seo maoin ''angular_velocity'' an chomhlachta dhocht chun "
"an corp a rothlú. Tugtar an ais chun rothlú timpeall ag an tras-táirge idir "
"an treo reatha ar aghaidh agus an treo is mian le duine chun breathnú "
"isteach. Is modh simplí é an ''clamp'' a úsáidtear chun cosc a chur ar an "
"méid uainíochta dul thar an treo a bhfuiltear ag iarraidh breathnú air, "
"toisc go dtugann arccosine an táirge ponc an méid iomlán uainíochta a "
"theastaíonn. Is féidir an modh seo a úsáid le ''axis_lock_angular_*'' chomh "
"maith. Má tá gá le rialú níos beaichte, d'fhéadfadh go mbeadh gá le réitigh "
"ar nós na cinn atá ag brath ar :ref:'class_Quaternion', mar a phléitear in :"
"ref:'doc_using_transforms'."
